data.description: A MUST SEE! BRAND NEW ROOF & GUTTERS! !  2200 sqf 3 BR 2 BTH home, on 1.01 acres in a nice quiet neighborhood. Property is completely fenced and gated.  Located in the north side of Brookings, within the Harris Beach neighborhood.  Very  spacious living room, bright  kitchen with a large island w/ Jenn Aire stove,  along with a walk in pantry.  Paved driveway, with plenty of room for RV's boats and toys.  Shop is 813 sqft.  Come check it out.
